screen_desc: A screenshot of a social media app's menu interface. The top section includes icons for home, video, marketplace, notifications, and a menu. Below, there is an option to "Create new profile or Page." The main menu options include "Memories," "Saved," "Groups," "Video," "Marketplace," "Friends (25 online)," "Feeds," and "Dating." There is a "See more" button, followed by sections for "Help & support," "Settings & privacy," "Also from Meta," and a "Log out" button at the bottom. The time displayed is 8:49, and the device shows a 4G connection with full signal and battery.
